                <note rend="inline" type="source">653.116/125: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Portugal (<persName type="to">Caldwell</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-11-08T20:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 8, 1933—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>12. Your despatch 68, October 23. Since it is expected that commercial treaty
                    discussions will be started in a day or so with the Portuguese Minister, I feel
                    that it will be better to delay for the time being the representations you
                    suggest making.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
